### Transition from paper to digital wireframes  

are you ready to move on to a digital wireframe?  
1、Is my paper wireframe complete?   
2、Have I received feedback on my paper wireframe?   
3、Am I ready to consider basic visual cues?   

创建 digital wireframe 的注意事项  
1、use actual content for important pieces of text, instead of all placeholder text. 重要的部位尽量使用真实的文案内容    
2、you should hold back on adding expressive content, like color or images, into your wireframe for now. 暂时不要添加过于丰富的内容，比如颜色或图片，专注线框的布局和功能性，先确保功能结构清晰      

from paper wireframe to digital wireframe, to get the structure right, making your design cleaner.  


